OL,3,CFire chief claims responding to fire
OL,4,Calarms is 'waste of resources'
OL,6,FWATCH: ITV News Meridian's Kit
OL,7,FBradshaw reports from Hastings Fire
OL,8,FStation
OL,10,FSending fire crews in response to
OL,11,Fautomatic alarms is a 'waste of
OL,12,Fresources' due to the 'high number of
OL,13,Ffalse alerts', according to East
OL,14,FSussex Fire and Rescue Service.
OL,16,FManagers have defended a decision to
OL,17,Fstop routinely dispatching crews to
OL,18,Finvestigate alarm activations.
