OL,3,CFire chief claims responding to fire
OL,4,Calarms is 'waste of resources'
OL,6,FThe change in policy means that from 1
OL,7,FApril 2024 firefighters will not be
OL,8,Fsent to low-risk commercial premises
OL,9,Fsuch as offices, shops, schools,
OL,10,Ffactories, pubs, clubs and restaurants.
OL,12,FThe new approach does not affect the
OL,13,Fway the service responds to incidents
OL,14,Fin homes or businesses with people
OL,15,Fsleeping on site, such as care homes
OL,16,Fand hotels.
