OL,3,CFire chief claims responding to fire
OL,4,Calarms is 'waste of resources'
OL,6,FThe Fire Brigades Union opposed the
OL,7,Fchange, while some businesses have
OL,8,Fexpressed concern about the impact.
OL,9,FHowever, fire chiefs have insisted the
OL,10,Fdecision is low-risk due to the number
OL,11,Fof false alarms.
OL,13,FArea Manager at East Sussex Fire &
OL,14,FRescue Service (ESFRS), George
OL,15,FO'Reilly, told ITV News: "That is a
OL,16,Fsignificant waste of our resources. On
OL,17,Faverage, we can spend about an hour
OL,18,Fper call and that's an hour that we
OL,19,Fcould use doing community safety
OL,20,Factivity.
