OL,6,FDervis Gurol owns and runs the Healthy
OL,7,FU Pharmacy in Saltdean, East Sussex.
OL,8,FHe said: "To be honest with you, it's
OL,9,Fkind of worrying. Reason being is I
OL,10,Fdon't think there was enough
OL,11,Fconsideration given to some properties
OL,12,Fthat may have a commercial unit
OL,13,Fdownstairs like our one that also has
OL,14,Fa different landlord that has got
OL,15,Fflats upstairs."
OL,17,FESFRS is urging those in charge of
OL,18,Faffected premises to take action to
OL,19,Fmake sure they are ready.
